    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver that presents decently from a distance but shows clear wear and age up close. Expect noticeable cosmetic flaws to the paint, body, trim, and interior, along with the kind of imperfections and deferred items common in an older, used car. It appears usable as-is for someone seeking an affordable entry point, but buyers should plan on some cleanup, repairs, and ongoing maintenance to bring it to a higher standard. Best suited for someone who wants a realistic driver rather than a show car.",
