      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced right for someone who wants affordable wheels or a project with potential. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for a handy buyer who appreciates good value. If you\u2019re after something cheap, usable, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
