    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget project or beater with a strong-running powertrain foundation and straightforward mechanical layout. It shows its age cosmetically and needs TLC, but it starts, moves, and offers a good platform for someone who knows their way around maintenance. Great candidate for a commuter-on-a-budget, weekend wrenching project, or parts donor with plenty of usable life in the core components.",
