    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for the right buyer, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads with its story rather than its shine. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone looking for an affordable set of wheels, a hands-on project, or a blank canvas to make their own. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that speaks to years of journeys and plenty more waiting ahead. If you appreciate substance, potential, and the thrill of giving a car its next chapter, this one is ready to be part of your story.",
